---

<Layout 
  title="South Portland Dispensary Guide" 
  description="South Portland Maine dispensary guide. Portland metro market analysis, local zoning, and OCP licensing requirements for 2026."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
